info.name: Dolphin{anty} Remote API Docs
info.description:
## Request limit is 500 requests per minute

About authorization

1. You should generate an API access token. Go to [https://anty.dolphin.ru.com/panel/#/api](https://anty.dolphin.ru.com/panel/#/api)
2. Fill name, select expiration days, and click the button to create a token. It's an opening popup you can copy the token. Make sure you save your token, as you won't be able to see it again.
3. You should provide this access token in each request in the Authorization -> Bearer Token

Array of users IDs to filter with. If not specifed only current user's browser profiles will be returned.
